thout any liable partner the german equivalent that comes closest to llc is gmbh  co kg a nested kommanditgesellschaft kg where a gesellschaft mit beschrÃ¤nkter haftung gmbh takes the role of the fully liable partner for the purpose of taxation the bundesfinanzministerium german federal ministry of finance gives detailed guidelines of the circumstances under which an llc is to be considered to be a corporation or as a limited partnership it is useful to note however that the original llc statutes of wyoming and other us states were more or less explicitly modeled after the gmbh greeceedit a limited liability company llc in greece is synonymous to an epe ÎµÏÎµ  ÎµÏÎ±Î¹ÏÎµÎ¯Î± ÏÎµÏÎ¹Î¿ÏÎ¹ÏÎ¼Î­Î½Î·Ï ÎµÏÎ¸ÏÎ½Î·Ï hong kongedit in hong kong the limited company is the most commonly incorporated type of company and bears the characteristics of a limited liability company the core characteristics of a hong kong limited company include i it requires a minimum of one shareholder and one director can be the same person ii a hong kong company requires a company secretary resident in hk iii foreign ownership is allowed iv company shareholders have limited liability and v the company must have registered hk address entrepreneurs who register a company in hong kong can choose a hong kong offshore company this company structure is basically a hk limited company but all business is conducted outside of hong kong the advantage of this structure is that all business income that is sourced outside of hong kong is tax exempt hungaryedit hungarian legislation contemplates llcs as korlÃ¡tolt felelÅssÃ©gÅ± tÃ¡rsasÃ¡g companies working under this structure append the abbreviation kft to their name hungarian llcs are required to have a  million huf hungarian forint approx  usd starting capital the time of formation by the new electronic formation option has been reduced from  weeks to  hours additional cost of formation is around  huf approx  usd kfts can be formed by the cooperat