hat the original llc statutes of wyoming and other us states were more or less explicitly modeled after the gmbh greeceedit a limited liability company llc in greece is synonymous to an epe ÎµÏÎµ  ÎµÏÎ±Î¹ÏÎµÎ¯Î± ÏÎµÏÎ¹Î¿ÏÎ¹ÏÎ¼Î­Î½Î·Ï ÎµÏÎ¸ÏÎ½Î·Ï hong kongedit in hong kong the limited company is the most commonly incorporated type of company and bears the characteristics of a limited liability company the core characteristics of a hong kong limited company include i it requires a minimum of one shareholder and one director can be the same person ii a hong kong company requires a company secretary resident in hk iii foreign ownership is allowed iv company shareholders have limited liability and v the company must have registered hk address entrepreneurs who register a company in hong kong can choose a hong kong offshore company this company structure is basically a hk limited company but all business is conducted outside of hong kong the advantage of this structure is that all business income that is sourced outside of hong kong is tax exempt hungaryedit hungarian legislation contemplates llcs as korlÃ¡tolt felelÅssÃ©gÅ± tÃ¡rsasÃ¡g companies working under this structure append the abbreviation kft to their name hungarian llcs are required to have a  million huf hungarian forint approx  usd starting capital the time of formation by the new electronic formation option has been reduced from  weeks to  hours additional cost of formation is around  huf approx  usd kfts can be formed by the cooperation of lawyers the hungarian kft is the most common form of doing business in hungary as being part of the european union eu hungarian kfts can now obtain an eu vat registration number for doing business across the eu the hungarian euvat reg number starts with hu this way the existence of the subject company vat issues and the crosscheck is available on the common eu website for companiescitation needed icelandedit according to icelandic legislation there are two type